snippet.title: Elon Musk SPEAKS On Rumors About Being Amber Heard's Baby's Father!!!
snippet.description:
Elon Musk SPEAKS On Rumors About Being Amber Heard's Baby's Father!!!

As if things with Amber Heard couldn’t get more confusing it just so happens to be that she dropped some insane news not too long ago. It turns out that Amber Heard is actually a mother? And actually had been for a couple of months already, which is a shock to many. On Thursday the 35 year old Aquaman actress announced this big news on her personal instagram. Heard went on to post a mother daughter photo of her now 12 week old baby. But the truth is, people are kind of confused as to who the other person in the picture is. At this point, anything is possible and it just seems to be that Heard is full of surprises so no one is sure as far as what to expect.
